Class DynamicBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.raiden.game.physics_controller.entities.DynamicBody
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BulletBody, CometBody, ShipBody

    public abstract class DynamicBody
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class that represents an abstract physical body supported by a Box2D body.
